用户问题：我的二分查找总是返回-1

用户提供的代码：
int binary_search(int arr[], int n, int target) {
    int left = 0, right = n;
    while (left < right) {
        int mid = (left + right) / 2;
        if (arr[mid] == target) return mid;
        else if (arr[mid] < target) left = mid;
        else right = mid;
    }
    return -1;
}

知识图谱关联：空

参考文档：空

有两个bug：
1. **区间定义不一致**：`right = n` 是右开区间，但 `left = mid` 按闭区间逻辑写
2. **死循环**：当 `left + 1 == right` 时，`mid = left`，`left = mid` 不变

**修复：统一左闭右开区间**
```c
int binary_search(int arr[], int n, int target) {
    int left = 0, right = n;
    while (left < right) {
        int mid = left + (right - left) / 2;
        if (arr[mid] == target) return mid;
        else if (arr[mid] < target) left = mid + 1;
        else right = mid;
    }
    return -1;
}
```

**调试方法：** 在循环内加 `printf("left=%d, right=%d, mid=%d\n", left, right, mid);` 观察变量变化。

